  "detailed_description": "<h1>Also Recommended</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>Motivational Hero is a Emotional and Motivational Puzzle-Platformer 2d with levels based in Motivational Analogies with a dinamic procedural color pallete system<br><br><strong>Features</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>16 Levels inspired in motivational messages</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A cheap and fast game that can be beated in a few minutes depending of your level skills </li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Relaxing, Motivational and Inspiring </li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Procedural Color Pallete System, each level and each try have a random pallete </li></ul><br><br>Relaxing Gameplay<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1732140/extras/14dd40f90e58adc00f97f727a9f6813f.poster.avif?t=1655406374\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1732140/extras/14dd40f90e58adc00f97f727a9f6813f.webm?t=1655406374\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1732140/extras/14dd40f90e58adc00f97f727a9f6813f.mp4?t=1655406374\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Analogies in every stage<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1732140/extras/8ad57d30ff323a8d42632ce4fdb93aba.poster.avif?t=1655406374\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1732140/extras/8ad57d30ff323a8d42632ce4fdb93aba.webm?t=1655406374\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1732140/extras/8ad57d30ff323a8d42632ce4fdb93aba.mp4?t=1655406374\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Maniac for Button